fields.name: Priority Overnight
fields.description: Morning, next business day to most metropolitan areas
fields.exceptions: 2 to 3 business days to other areas. Saturday: most major cities in Canada and select international points

fields.name: First Overnight
fields.description: 10 a.m. next business day to most metropolitan areas
fields.exceptions: Saturday service: pickup only. Limited locations. Saturday: most major cities in Canada and select international points

fields.name: Standard Overnight

fields.exceptions: Saturday service: pickup only. Limited locations. Saturday: most major cities in Canada and select international points

fields.exceptions: Saturday: most major cities in Canada and select international points

fields.name: Economy

fields.name: Ground
fields.description: 1 to 7 business days

fields.name: Expedited Parcel
fields.description: Delivery Guarantee with Delivery Confirmation

fields.name: Xpresspost

fields.exceptions: National: 2 days

fields.exceptions: National: 2 days

fields.name: Priority
fields.description: Next day

fields.name: International First
fields.description: 1, 2, or 3 business days to select postal codes in 20 key global markets
fields.exceptions: Saturday service: pickup only, limited locations, and additional charge. Delivery by 10 a.m. in 1 business day to Canada. 11 a.m. in 1 business day to Mexico (2 business days for nondocument shipments)

fields.name: International Economy
fields.description: 2–5 business days (typically 2 or 3 business days to Canada, Mexico and Puerto Rico)
fields.exceptions: Saturday service: available in countries where Saturday is a regular business day

fields.name: International Priority
fields.description: 1, 2 or 3 business days
fields.exceptions: Canada and Mexico typically in 1 business day, and major cities in Europe, Asia and Brazil by noon typically in 2 business days

fields.name: International 9AM
fields.description: Guaranteed delivery to and from select international destinations by 9 a.m. the second business day
fields.exceptions: End of day is 6 p.m

fields.name: International 10:30AM
fields.description: Guaranteed delivery to and from select international destinations by 10:30 a.m. the second business day
fields.exceptions: End of day is 6 p.m

fields.name: International 12PM
fields.description: Guaranteed delivery from select points in Canada to international destinations by 12 p.m. (noon) the second business day
fields.exceptions: End of day is 6 p.m

fields.name: International
fields.description: Guaranteed delivery to and from most international destinations by the second business day
fields.exceptions: End of day is 6 p.m

fields.description: 4-7 day delivery
fields.exceptions: Duties and taxes collected from receiver

fields.description: 4-7 days delivery to a limited number of countries
